    {
      "id": "era1-events", "type": "text", "x": 45, "y": 165, "width": 230, "height": 180,
      "text": "2022.06  GitHub Copilot 출시\n2022.11  ChatGPT 공개\n2022.01  Chain-of-Thought\n2022.10  ReAct\n2023.03  Cursor 등장\n2023.05  Tree-of-Thought\n2024.03  Ng 4 Patterns\n2024.12  Anthropic Agents 가이드\n\n엄밀함 위치: 프롬프트 텍스트\n 사인: Blind Prompting",
